<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.1.6">
<l>ōtuvā rōttellā mevvulakat tevvevaiyum</l>
<l>cātāy niṉpukaḻiṉ ṟakaiyallāl piṟitillai</l>
<l>pōtuvāḻ puṉantuḻāy muṭiyiṉāy pūviṉmēṉ</l>
<l>mātuvāḻ mārpiṉā yeṉcollināṉ vāḻttuvaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Being all the reciters’ recitations, every and any thing in any world,</l>
<l>good, there is nothing but the fitness of your praise.</l>
<l>You with a crown of field Tulsi in which buds live, you with a chest</l>
<l>on which the woman on the flower lives, saying what shall I praise you?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
